OpenSecrets.org Data

Welcome to the world of Big Money in Politics and Public Policy!  We at the Center for Responsive Politics and our web site OpenSecrets.org are pleased to provide this data for you via Sunlightâ€™s Influence Explorer tool.  This itemized detailed data is not always easy to use correctly, and you can find lots of helpful information to make it easier to do so at http://www.OpenSecrets.org/resources/create/data_doc.php 

Please remember that this data is provided free only for non-commercial use by not-for-profit institutions and individuals under Creative Commons BY-NC-SA license.  To inquire about commercial use, please email apis@crp.org.  

Proper attribution or citation when using these data is to the Center for Responsive Politics, and you can find attribution information and logos online at http://www.opensecrets.org/resources/create/credit.php

